Podcast Data Scrapping

"At 'Freakonomics', podcasts are readily accessible and provided for free, allowing listeners to access both audio content and written scripts."

https://freakonomics.com/

You can scrap podcast scripts in textual form and use them for your shared task using the provided Python script.

Instructions to use Python script to scrap podcast data:
    1.	First, make sure you have the required libraries installed:
        a.	pip install requests
        b.	pip install beautifulsoup4
    2.	Provide URL for a particular podcast – line 5
    3.	Provide path and file name to save podcast title and description – line 31
    4.	Provide path and file name to save podcast script – line 56
